headline: 7 Stocks I'm Buying In Defiance Of Post-Election Euphoria
summary: There is a dangerous euphoria in certain stock sectors. Here's my dividend stock buy list, which have not enjoyed even a little bit of the post-election optimism.

headline: SEC Collects Record $8.2 Billion in Financial Penalties in 2024
summary: The Securities and Exchange Commission said it collected $8.2 billion in monetary penalties for the fiscal year 2024, the highest amount for the fines in the regulator’s history.
